Class BukkitPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pwn9.filter.bukkit.BukkitPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageAuthor, BurnTarget, FineTarget, KickTarget, KillTarget

    public class BukkitPlayer
extends Object
implements MessageAuthor, FineTarget, BurnTarget, KillTarget, KickTarget
    Author of a text string sent to us by Bukkit. This is typically a player. These objects are transient, and only last for as long as the message does.

    Created by Sage905 on 15-08-31.
